{"tid":1716514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三罷唔可以停","createTime":"2019-11-13T11:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:16:58.000Z","uid":135406,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"318bc4f25111fd2a8d320774cb7e72138e89122d","tid":1716514,"uid":135406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:00:53.000Z","msg":"仲猶疑緊參唔參加黎明行動既和理非/淺黃，請聽小弟一言<br />\n<br />\n連續三日既三罷係前所未有，效果亦都非常顯著，呢個政權最大既春袋一直都係經濟，如果可以做到無限期既三罷，相信佢好快會跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三罷亦都係其中一個最低成本換最高效益既手段，曾經係炎炎夏日，甚至冒住大雨出黎遊行既你，點解唔試下早啲起身同手足一齊塞交通呢，呢個與民為敵既殺人政權，唔係話你去遊行，去求佢，佢就會答應我地既訴求，見到前線手足中實彈差啲連命都無，你仲忍心係到口號式抗爭咩<br />\n<br />\n要記住我地已經無野可以再輸，今次長期既三罷如果輸左，你有信心下次仲可以做到一樣咁大既規模?我敢肯定一定更難，阻力一定會更大，所以如果睇完篇文令你想做多啲野既，求下你幫推去reach到更多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人 反抗! 報仇!"},{"pid":"7d6d513d6449ac09369b2988c75e35b3bb1b2f53","tid":1716514,"uid":135211,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:04:52.000Z","msg":"最緊要係氣勢如虹 冇可能停<br />\n一停 班要推先郁嘅人就消失"},{"pid":"66ee7070e54831e39a9305acc69daed2425c95b0","tid":1716514,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"717fa8a511211f668dd5a686f1be0b615458b0ce","tid":1716514,"uid":163761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddd205c420af3e896ece020916e3e11aaac7f773","tid":1716514,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:05:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續啊繼續啊繼續啊繼續到落實五大訴求煲底相見啊屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民同我早早早早早起，繼續無限三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人已經退無可退！Neve forgive. Never forget. </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VsHV0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VsHV0b.jpg&h=53f43c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdzLMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdzLMW.jpg&h=f251c786&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be299a09ab18fedb73414acd5ef5b5d800580c77","tid":1716514,"uid":163761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c9d0716c033bddbd4261a3065e24991b4f1e1fe","tid":1716514,"uid":67813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"中大件事係一個轉捩點"},{"pid":"27aabdbb67bafd3b569b5b0dec1a3da306009a40","tid":1716514,"uid":12222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"feel 到大家開始放鬆左<br />\n小心呀 唔可以輕敵<br />\n佢地要整死我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3a4815cd0935994a825be92db57d397ab749b8","tid":1716514,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6203c53875fd1554b0ba5659be30f9eceab38bd","tid":1716514,"uid":6468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:09:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be56c43eedd1fa3e3fec68df57d32b1a4db01645","tid":1716514,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27aabdbb67bafd3b569b5b0dec1a3da306009a40","tid":1716514,"uid":12222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"feel 到大家開始放鬆左<br />\n小心呀 唔可以輕敵<br />\n佢地要整死我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"我地游車河再返工啫。<br />\n總結經驗：今日係塞到停鐵，從而達至成功。我地再接再厲，繼續塞到佢暫停，加油！"},{"pid":"18bc27f1b96a63903cbce0c5b86a43d08a497cdc